  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Idle Animal Plaza, an idle district management simulator. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will play the role of an up-and-coming entrepreneur responsible for managing the local restaurants. You will open shops of various kinds to develop your district, at the same time managing their internal operations. The fate of the district is in your hands! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Features: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/682795b0adcb55a2d5f08336ff6b36c8.avif?t=1728891235\" width=600 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from different food and beverage shops, selling varied dishes such as burgers, coffee, and donuts, with many restaurant themes to choose from! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/cc1d1e29495d7a33d43e28685ecd5ecd.poster.avif?t=1728891235\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/cc1d1e29495d7a33d43e28685ecd5ecd.webm?t=1728891235\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/cc1d1e29495d7a33d43e28685ecd5ecd.mp4?t=1728891235\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/69247fe27927e3b41c45ad4a7c32b5a5.avif?t=1728891235\" width=600 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the Capsule Machine to unlock more dishes. Each shop has 20 special dishes to choose from. The more dishes you unlock, the more your profits will skyrocket! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/fa668d25b482fdfdade6855fc28f4efe.poster.avif?t=1728891235\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/fa668d25b482fdfdade6855fc28f4efe.webm?t=1728891235\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/fa668d25b482fdfdade6855fc28f4efe.mp4?t=1728891235\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/c1f77a22df5740bea2017c4b8faf06ce.avif?t=1728891235\" width=600 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruiting a manager is the first step when opening a new shop. Train your manager by upgrading your dishes; as their level increases, you will gain more shop privileges!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/d850b7d9a53064ea5682a6e9c418f912.poster.avif?t=1728891235\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/d850b7d9a53064ea5682a6e9c418f912.webm?t=1728891235\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/d850b7d9a53064ea5682a6e9c418f912.mp4?t=1728891235\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/db300eb0bc7fd3552d25e305d2ab016d.avif?t=1728891235\" width=600 height=128 /></span>Enjoy exciting mini-games such as Matching and Fruit Relay!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >         <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/a5be7792cda5d2232bb4f4f700ba167e.poster.avif?t=1728891235\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/a5be7792cda5d2232bb4f4f700ba167e.webm?t=1728891235\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/a5be7792cda5d2232bb4f4f700ba167e.mp4?t=1728891235\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As long as you put your heart into it, your district is sure to thrive! Set your sights on becoming the ultimate entrepreneur! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- What are you waiting for? Join Idle Animal Plaza and experience a different kind of business management simulator!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- More unique shop types and new districts coming soon!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Idle Animal Plaza, an idle district management simulator. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will play the role of an up-and-coming entrepreneur responsible for managing the local restaurants. You will open shops of various kinds to develop your district, at the same time managing their internal operations. The fate of the district is in your hands! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Features: </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/682795b0adcb55a2d5f08336ff6b36c8.avif?t=1728891235\" width=600 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from different food and beverage shops, selling varied dishes such as burgers, coffee, and donuts, with many restaurant themes to choose from! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >          <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/cc1d1e29495d7a33d43e28685ecd5ecd.poster.avif?t=1728891235\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/cc1d1e29495d7a33d43e28685ecd5ecd.webm?t=1728891235\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/cc1d1e29495d7a33d43e28685ecd5ecd.mp4?t=1728891235\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211780/extras/69247fe27927e3b41c45ad4a7c32b5a5.avif?t=1728891235\" width=600 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the Capsule Machine to unlock more dishes. Each shop has 20 special dishes to choose from. The more dishes you unlock, the more your profits will skyrocket! </p><p c